[SN]TITLE[SN]
Marcus' top advice for keeping a tech balance

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Gadgets are playing a bigger and bigger role in our lives but although they are fun, sometimes they can become a bit of an obsession.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
24 March 2016 Last updated at 09:14 GMT
We caught up with Technobabble's Marcus, to find out how he balances seeing his friends with playing on his gadgets.
Being tech savvy is great, but so is hanging out with your mates, take a peek at Marcus's top tips and advice for finding a balance.
